---
title: Alpine Mushroom & Swiss Panini with Asparagus & Garlic Aioli
description: Once deemed “lunch food only,” sandwiches (better yet, panini) like this one could not be more dinner-worthy—it features sautéed mushrooms and onion, tangy Dijon mustard, and not one, but TWO types of cheese (Swiss and Monterey Jack) between slices of sourdough and pan-pressed to crispy, golden perfection. On the side, there are potato wedges and garlicky aioli for dipping. Step aside, lunch police!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/63e3d3d6f5a9744aec0b3ca5-86ee4630.jpg
